name: Megalith Phuloch
desc:
You can Ritual Summon this card with any "Megalith" card. You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn. You cannot activate the ① and ② effect of this card's name in the same Chain.
①：If this card is Ritual Summoned: You can add 1 "Megalith" card from your GY to your hand.
②：During the Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can Ritual Summon 1 "Megalith" Ritual Monster from your GY, except "Megalith Phuloch", by Tributing monsters from your hand and/or field whose total Levels equal or exceed the Level of that monster, including this card on the field.

name: Megalith Nortra Phulra
desc:
You can Ritual Summon this card with any "Megalith" card. Must be Ritual Summoned, using only Ritual Monsters. You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can reveal this card in your hand; your opponent cannot activate cards or effects in response to the activation of your "Megalith" Ritual Monsters' effects for the rest of this turn.
②：When your opponent activates a card or effect (Quick Effect): You can negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that card, then, if that effect targeted a card(s) on the field, you can Tribute 1 monster your opponent controls.

name: Megalith Anastasis
desc:
You can only use the ① effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：You can discard 1 card; add 1 Level 4 or lower and 1 Level 8 or higher "Megalith" monsters from your Deck to your hand.
②：Once per turn, if you Ritual Summon a "Megalith" monster(s): You can activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each of these effects of this card's name once per turn).
● Draw 2 cards, then discard 1 card.
● Tribute 1 monster your opponent controls.

name: Magnifistorming Megala
desc:
You can only Special Summon with the ① effect of this card's name once per turn. You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If you have "Mystical Space Typhoon" in your GY, or your opponent controls no Spells/Traps, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand).
②：If a "Magnifistorm" Quick-Play Spell or "Mystical Space Typhoon" is activated: You can Special Summon 1 "Magnifistorm" monster from your Deck with a different name from the monsters you control, also you cannot Special Summon for the rest of this turn, except WIND monsters.

name: Magnifistorming Erdam
desc:
You can only Special Summon with the ① effect of this card's name once per turn. You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If you have "Mystical Space Typhoon" in your GY, or your opponent controls no Spells/Traps, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand).
②：If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Magnifistorm" monster or "Mystical Space Typhoon" from your Deck to your hand, except "Magnifistorming Erdam".

name: Magnifistorming Suen
desc:
You can only Special Summon with the ① effect of this card's name once per turn. You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If you have "Mystical Space Typhoon" in your GY, or your opponent controls no Spells/Traps, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand).
②：If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Magnifistorm" Spell/Trap or "Mystical Space Typhoon" from your Deck to your hand.

name: Magnifistorming Crothea
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If a Quick-Play Spell Card is activated: You can Special Summon this card from your hand.
②：If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Magnifistorm" card and/or 1 "Mystical Space Typhoon" from your Deck and/or GY to your hand, except "Magnifistorming Crothea", also you cannot Special Summon for the rest of this turn, except WIND monsters.
③：Cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects while your opponent controls no Spells/Traps.

name: Magnifistorm Vortex Beauty Valrune
desc:
You can only use the ①, ②, and ③ effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If a Quick-Play Spell Card is activated: You can Special Summon this card from your hand.
②：When your opponent activates a monster effect and you have "Mystical Space Typhoon" in your GY (Quick Effect): You can negate that effect, then, if you have 2 or more "Mystical Space Typhoon" in your GY, you can destroy that monster.
③：If "Mystical Space Typhoon" is activated while this card is in your GY: You can Special Summon it.

name: Magnifistorm Great Pyre Phonix
desc:
You can only use the ①, ②, and ③ effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If a Quick-Play Spell Card is activated: You can Special Summon this card from your hand.
②：If a Quick-Play Spell Card is activated: You can target up to 2 cards your opponent controls; shuffle them into the Deck.
③：If "Mystical Space Typhoon" is activated while this card is in your GY: You can Special Summon it.

name: Magnifistorming Stanza Tribute
desc:
①：Activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each of these effects of this card name's effect once per turn);
● Add 1 Level 4 or lower "Magnifistorm" monster from your Deck to your hand.
● Add 1 "Mystical Space Typhoon" from your Deck or GY to your hand.
②：If this card is destroyed by the effect of "Mystical Space Typhoon": You can Set this card.

name: Magnifistorming Summoning Technique
desc:
①：Activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each of these effects of this card's name once per turn);
● Send 1 "Magnifistorm" monster from your Deck to the GY.
● Add 1 "Mystical Space Typhoon" from your Deck or GY to your hand.
②：If this card is destroyed by the effect of "Mystical Space Typhoon": You can Set this card.

name: Magnifistorming Sight Trance
desc:
①：Activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each of these effects of this card name's effect once per turn);
● Draw 2 cards, then discard 1 "Magnifistorm" card or Quick-Play Spell, or, if you do not have any in your hand, discard your entire hand.
● Add 1 "Mystical Space Typhoon" from your Deck or GY to your hand.
②：If this card is destroyed by the effect of "Mystical Space Typhoon": You can Set this card.

name: Magnifistorming Sovereign Tyranny
desc:
①：Once per turn: You can target 3 Quick-Play Spells in your GY, including a "Magnifistorm" card; apply these effects, in sequence.
● Shuffle them into the Deck, then draw 1 card.
● WIND monsters you control will gain 300 ATK/DEF for the rest of this turn.
②：Once per Chain, when "Mystical Space Typhoon" is activated: You can target 1 face-up card your opponent controls; negate its effects.
③：If this card is destroyed by the effect of "Mystical Space Typhoon": You can Set this card.

name: Gouki Mashin Suprex
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can reveal this card and 1 other "Gouki" monster in your hand; Special Summon both, but you cannot Special Summon while you control either of those monsters, except "Gouki" monsters.
②：If this card is sent from the field to the GY: You can add 1 "Gouki" card from your Deck to your hand, except "Gouki Mashin Suprex".

name: Gouki The Tyrant Ogre
desc:
1 "Gouki" Link Monster + 1 Warrior, Dinosaur, or Cyberse monster
You can only use the ① effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If this card is Fusion Summoned: You can target cards on the field, up to the total Link Ratings of the "Gouki" Link Monsters used as material; destroy them. If you used a Link-3 or higher monster as material, those cards cannot be activated in response to this effect's activation.
②：If this card battles, your opponent cannot activate card or effects until the end of the Damage Step.

name: Gouki Dragon Ogre
desc:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If this card is Synchro Summoned: You can add 1 "Gouki" Spell from your Deck to your hand.
②：If this card is sent to the GY: You can target 1 EARTH monster you control; add 1 "Gouki" monster with lower ATK from your GY to your hand, also, while the targeted monster is face-up on your field, your opponent's monsters can only target that monster for attacks.

name: Gouki Sheik Ogre
desc:
2 "Gouki" monsters
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If a "Gouki" monster(s) is added from the Deck to your hand, except by drawing it: You can Special Summon any number of "Gouki" monsters from your hand with different Levels from each other, but you cannot Special Summon while you control any of those face-up monsters, except "Gouki" monsters.
②：During your Main Phase: You can Fusion Summon 1 "Gouki" Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, using monsters from your hand or field as material.

name: Gouki Fighting Spirit
desc:
You can only activate 1 card with this card's name per turn. You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：When this card resolves, you can Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower EARTH monster (Warrior, Dinosaur, or Cyberse) from your hand in Defense Position.
②：You can Tribute 1 Link-3 or higher "Gouki" monster; Special Summon 1 "Dinowrestler" or "G Golem" monster from your Deck or Extra Deck.

name: Sanaki the Mikanko Devotee
desc:
You can only use the ①, ②, and ③ effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can target 1 "Mikanko" card you control; return it to the hand.
②：If either player equips an Equip Card(s) to this card: You can Special Summon 1 non-Illusion "Mikanko" monster from your Deck, also you cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except "Mikanko" monsters.
③：If this card is sent to the GY: You can target 1 face-up monster on the field; equip this card to it.

name: Uzuhime the Manifested Mikanko
desc:
2 Level 3 "Mikanko" monsters
You can only use the ① effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If this card is Special Summoned: You can add 1 Equip Spell from your Deck or GY to your hand.
②：Cannot be destroyed by battle, also your opponent takes any battle damage you would have taken from battles involving this card.
③：If this card attacks, at the end of the Damage Step: You can detach 1 material from this card; it can make another attack in a row.

name: Mikanko Divine Dance – Futahashira no Uzu no Miko
desc:
You can only use 1 of the ① and ② effect of this card's name per turn, and only once that turn.
①：You cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn after this card resolves, except "Mikanko" monsters, also send 1 "Mikanko" card from your Deck to the GY, except "Mikanko Divine Dance – Futahashira no Uzu no Miko", then you can Set 1 "Mikanko" Spell/Trap from your Deck, except "Mikanko Divine Dance – Futahashira no Uzu no Miko".
②：You can banish this card from your GY and detach 1 Xyz Material from your monsters; Special Summon 1 "Mikanko" Ritual Monster from your hand or Deck.

name: Nurikabe
desc:
You can only use the effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If this card is in your GY, except the turn it was sent there: You can pay 1000 LP, then target 1 other Zombie monster in your GY; Special Summon it and this card, but their effects are negated, also banish them when they leave the field.

name: Dark Magic Amulet
desc:
You can activate this card the turn it was Set by revealing 1 Spellcaster monster in your hand.
①：When a monster effect is activated in response to the activation of a card that mentions "Dark Magician" or its effect: You can negate that effect, and if you do, for the rest of this turn, the activated effects of monsters with the same original name are negated.
②：If you Special Summon "Dark Magician" while this card is in your GY: You can pay 2500 LP; Set this card.

name: Dragonic Warrior
desc:
You can only use the effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：You can discard 1 card; Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Dragon monster from your hand or Deck, except "Dragonic Warrior", but its effects are negated.

name: Einroid
desc:
You can only use the effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If this card is destroyed by battle or card effect: You can send 2 Level 4 or lower Machine monsters from your Deck to the GY.

name: D/D Lance Soldier
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can target 1 "D/D" monster you control; increase its Level by up to the number of "Dark Contract" cards you control and in your GY.
②：If this card is in your GY: You can target 1 "Dark Contract" card you control; destroy it, and if you do, Special Summon this card, but banish it when it leaves the field.

name: D/D Defense Soldier
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Target 1 "D/D" card in your Pendulum Zone; Special Summon it.
● Banish 1 "D/D" monster from your GY; if your "D/D/D" monster attacks this turn, your opponent cannot activate cards or effects until the end of the Damage Step.
②：You can banish this card from your GY; add 1 "D/D" Pendulum Monster from your face-up Extra Deck or GY to your hand.

name: D/D/D Zero Demise King Zero Machinex
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 0
[Pendulum Effect]
You can only use the Pendulum Effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：During your Main Phase, if this card was activated this turn: You can place 1 "Dark Contract" Continuous Spell/Trap from your Deck face-up on your field.
----------------------------------------
[Monster Effect]
You can only use the ① and ② monster effects of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If a face-up "D/D/D" and/or "Dark Contract" card(s) you control is destroyed while this card is face-up in your Extra Deck (even during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card, then you can destroy 1 card on the field.
②：If this card in the Monster Zone is destroyed: You can place it in your Pendulum Zone.

name: D/D/D/D Great Dimension King Arc Crisis
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 13
[Pendulum Effect]
You can only use the Pendulum Effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：You can target any number of "Dark Contract" cards you control; destroy them, then Special Summon up to that many "Doom King" Pendulum Monsters from your Deck and/or Extra Deck.
----------------------------------------
[Monster Effect]
4 Fiend monsters (1 Fusion, 1 Synchro, 1 Xyz, 1 Pendulum)
This face-down card in the Extra Deck must first be either Fusion Summoned, or Special Summoned by banishing the above cards from your field and/or GY. You can only Special Summon "D/D/D/D Great Dimension King Arc Crisis" once per turn this way, no matter which method you use.
①：If this card is Special Summoned: You can negate the effects of all face-up monsters your opponent currently controls.
②：Can attack all opponent's monsters once each.
③：If this card in the Monster Zone is destroyed: You can place it in your Pendulum Zone.

name: D/D/D Founder King Clovis
desc:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
You can only use the ① effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If this card is Synchro Summoned: You can target 1 of your banished "D/D" monsters, or, if you control a "Dark Contract" card, you can target 1 in your GY instead; Special Summon it.
②：If this card becomes banished: You can activate this effect; if your "D/D" monsters attacks a Defense Position monster this turn, inflict piercing battle damage.

name: D/D/D Wisdom King Solomon
desc:
2 Level 4 "D/D" monsters
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can detach 1 material from this card; add 1 "D/D" card from your Deck to your hand.
②：If this card becomes banished: You can target 1 "D/D" Effect Monster you control; that Effect Monster gains this effect until the end of this turn.
● If this card destroys a monster by battle: Inflict damage to your opponent equal to half that monster's original ATK.

name: D/D/D Sky King Zeus Ragnarok
desc:
2+ "D/D" Monsters
You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn each.
①：You can target 1 "D/D" or "Dark Contract" card you control; destroy it, also, during your Main Phase this turn, you can conduct 1 Pendulum Summon of a "D/D" monster(s) in addition to your Pendulum Summon. (You can only gain this effect once per turn.)
②：When your opponent activates a monster effect in the hand (Quick Effect): You can banish 1 "D/D" monster and 1 "Dark Contract" card from your GY; negate the activation.

name: Dark Contract with the Zero King
desc:
This card is always treated as a "D/D" card. You can only use the ① effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：You can target 1 "D/D" card you control, except "Dark Contract with the Zero King"; you cannot Special Summon for the rest of this turn, except "D/D" monsters, also destroy that card, and if you do, Special Summon 1 "D/D" monster from your Deck.
②：Once per turn, during your Standby Phase: Take 1000 damage.

name: Dark Contract with the Different Dimension
desc:
You can only use the ① and ③ effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can shuffle 2 "Dark Contract" cards from your GY into the Deck, then target 1 card your opponent controls or in their GY; banish it.
②：Once per turn, during your Standby Phase: Take 1000 damage.
③：If this card is destroyed: You can gain 500 LP, then, if it was destroyed by an opponent's card effect, you gain 500 LP.

name: Masked HERO Dusk Crow
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If this card is in your hand: You can banish 1 "HERO" monster from your GY; Special Summon this card.
②：If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Masked HERO" monster from your Deck or GY to your hand, except "Masked HERO Dusk Crow".

name: Masked HERO Furnace
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can reveal this card in your hand; add 1 "Mask Change" or "Polymerization" from your Deck to your hand, then discard 1 card. You cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck the turn you activate this effect, except "HERO" monsters.
②：If you Special Summon a non-FIRE "HERO" Fusion Monster(s): You can Special Summon this card from your GY (if it was there when the monster was Summoned) or hand (even if not), but banish it when it leaves the field.

name: Masked HERO Atomic
desc:
Must be Special Summoned with "Mask Change". You can only use the ① and ③ effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If this card is Special Summoned: You can target 1 non-FIRE "Masked HERO" monster in your GY or banishment; Special Summon it in Defense Position, ignoring its Summoning conditions.
②：The first time this card would be destroyed by battle or card effect each turn, it is not destroyed.
③：During your End Phase: You can target 1 "Change" Quick-Play Spell in your GY; Set it.

name: Dark Magician of Destruction
desc:
"Dark Magician" + 1 LIGHT or DARK monster
Must be either Fusion Summoned, or Special Summoned (from your Extra Deck) by banishing 1 Level 6 or higher DARK Spellcaster monster you control during the turn a Spell Card or effect was previously activated. You can only Special Summon "Dark Magician of Destruction" once per turn this way, no matter which method you use.
①：This card's name becomes "Dark Magician" while face-up on the field or in the GY.
②：If this card is Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Dark Magician" or 1 card that mentions it from your Deck to your hand.

name: Timaeus the United Magidragon
desc:
"Dark Magician" or "Dark Magician Girl" + 1 Dragon or Spellcaster monster
You can only use the ② and ③ effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：After this card is Special Summoned, until the end of your next turn, it is unaffected by other cards' effects.
②：If this card battles, during damage calculation: You can make it gain 100 ATK for each Spell in the GYs and banishment.
③：During your opponent's turn (Quick Effect): You can target 1 Spell/Trap on the field; destroy it.

name: The Gaze of Timaeus
desc:
You can only activate 1 card with this card's name per turn.
①：Target 1 "Dark Magician" or "Dark Magician Girl" you control or in your GY; Fusion Summon 1 Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck that mentions it as material, by shuffling that monster into the Deck, but banish it during the End Phase of the next turn. (This is treated as a Special Summon with "The Eye of Timaeus".)

name: Elemental HERO Thunder Giant – Voltic Thunder
desc:
2 "Elemental HERO" monsters with different Attributes
Must be Fusion Summoned. You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：If this card is Special Summoned and your opponent controls more cards than you do: You can destroy all other cards on the field.
②：You can Tribute this card Fusion Summoned using a Normal Monster as material, then target 1 "Elemental HERO" monster in your GY; Special Summon it.

name: Drill Armed Dragon
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①：You can send this card and 1 other WIND monster from your hand to the GY; for the rest of this turn, all WIND Dragon monster you control will gain 300 ATK.
②：You can banish any number of Dragon monsters that are Level 7 or higher and/or WIND from your GY; add 1 Dragon monster from your Deck to your hand with a Level equal to the number banished, except "Drill Armed Dragon".

name: Light Water Dragon
desc:
This card's name is always treated as "Water Dragon". You can only use the effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：You can banish this card you control; Special Summon 3 Level 5 or lower WATER and/or WIND Dinosaur monsters from your Deck in Defense Position, but their effects are negated, also you cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except Dinosaur and Sea Serpent monsters.

name: Soul Union
desc:
You can only activate 1 card with this card's name per turn.
①: Target 1 face-up monster on the field and 1 "Elemental HERO" monster in your GY; that monster on the field gains ATK equal to the ATK of other monster (until the end of this turn), then, if you have an "Elemental HERO" Normal Monster on your field and/or in your GY, you can Fusion Summon 1 "Elemental HERO" Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, by banishing its material from your GY.

name: Prima Light
desc:
You can only use 1 of the ① and ② effect of this card's name per turn, and only once that turn.
①: Activate 1 of these effects;
● Tribute 1 EARTH Warrior monster, and if you do, Special Summon 1 LIGHT Warrior monster from your hand or Deck.
● During the Main Phase: Immediately after this effect resolves, Normal Summon 1 Warrior monster from your hand.
②: During your Main Phase: You can banish this card from your GY; add 1 Warrior or Fairy "Cyber" monster from your Deck to your hand.

name: Conduction Warrior Linear Magnum ±
desc:
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand) by sending 2 "Magnet Warrior" monsters whose original Level is 4 or lower from your hand, Deck, and/or face-up field to the GY. You can only Special Summon "Conduction Warrior Linear Magnum ±" once per turn this way. You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①: You can target 1 other EARTH monster on the field; this card gains ATK equal to half that monster's until the end of this turn.
②: If this card is destroyed and sent to the GY: Add it to your hand.

name: Chaos Distill
desc:
You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: Any card sent to your GY is banished instead.
②: You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Add 1 "Macro Cosmos", or 1 card that mentions it, from your Deck to your hand, except "Chaos Distill".
● If "Macro Cosmos" is on the field: Banish this face-up card from the Spell & Trap Zone; add 1 LIGHT monster with ? ATK from your Deck to your hand.

name: Hero's Rule 1: Five Freedoms
desc:
You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: Target up to 5 cards in any GY(s); banish them.
②: If this card is in your GY, except the turn it was sent there: You can banish it, then target 1 of your banished "Elemental HERO" monsters; Special Summon it, ignoring its Summoning conditions.

name: Archfiend Matador
desc:
You can Ritual Summon this card with "Ritual of the Matador". You can only use the ① effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: If this card is Ritual Summoned: You can add 2 "Archfiend" cards from your Deck to your hand, except "Archfiend Matador", also this card cannot attack this turn.
②: Cannot be destroyed by battle, also you take no battle damage from battles involving this card.
③: If this card battles a monster, after damage calculation: Destroy that monster, and if you do, inflict 1000 damage to your opponent.

name: Ritual of the Matador
desc:
You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: Ritual Summon 1 "Archfiend Matador" from your hand, by Tributing monsters from your hand and/or field whose total Levels equal 6 or more.
②: You can banish this card from your GY; Special Summon 1 non-Ritual "Archfiend" monster from your hand.

name: Maiden in Love
desc:
①: Opponent's monsters that can attack this card must attack it.
②: Cannot be destroyed by battle.
③: If this card battles an opponent's monster, at the end of the Damage Step: You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Place 1 Maiden Counter on 1 face-up monster your opponent controls.
● Take control of 1 opponent's monster with a Maiden Counter.

name: Eucalyptus Mole
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effects of this card's name each once per turn.
①: If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Beast monster from your Deck in face-down Defense Position, then, if this card is in Attack Position, change it to Defense Position.
②: If this card is destroyed: You can Special Summon 1 "Koala" monster or 1 "Tree Otter" from your Deck, and if you do, apply this effect until the end of the next turn.
● Non-Effect Beast monsters you control gain ATK equal to their own original DEF.

name: Illusion Gate
desc:
You can only apply the effect of this card's name once per Duel.
①: Pay half your LP; destroy as many monsters your opponent controls as possible, then you can Special Summon 1 monster from their GY to your field, ignoring its Summoning conditions.
